rows.label: campfev11_320_150_msg0001
rows.name:
Ugh, I'm really not so keen on
boarding that flagship...

rows.label: campfev11_320_150_msg0002
rows.name:
Relax. I don't think it'll be as uptight
on there as you'd expect.

rows.label: campfev11_320_150_msg0003
rows.name:
You think?
Well, if you say so.

rows.label: campfev11_320_150_msg0006
rows.name:
Oh, just a certain snob who's always
giving me the stink-eye because I'm
not "acting with the proper decorum".

rows.label: campfev11_320_150_msg0008
rows.name:
Ah. Right. I can see Kagutsuchi
being strict on etiquette...

rows.label: campfev11_320_150_msg0009
rows.name:
Yeah, I'm not so hot on all that stuff.
So I tread carefully.
